Class ContactAddedCallback

java.lang.Object
  com.bulletphysics.ContactAddedCallback

public abstract class ContactAddedCallback
extends java.lang.Object

Called when contact has been created between two collision objects. At least one of object must have CollisionFlags.CUSTOM_MATERIAL_CALLBACK flag set.
